@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_geitui(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = v1
    v1 = v1
    v0 = wp.sin(((v0 + 0.82 * v2 + 0.59) + (v1 + 0.82 * v2 + 0.69)))
    v2 = wp.cos(wp.exp(0.43))
    v1 = (0.80 + tmp)
    data[tid] = v0
